lu.uni.geko.commands The commands package of the main plug-in for GeKo, a generic model weaver. 
 

Classes in lu.uni.geko.commands used by lu.uni.geko.commands
AbstractEcoreFilesHandler
          An abstract handler for commands that are only available if Ecore metamodels have been selected.
AbstractFileHandler
          An abstract handler for commands that discriminate selected files based on their type and create a Runnable for the selected files.
AbstractFolderHandler
          An abstract handler for commands that only take selected folders into account.
AbstractSingleFileTypeHandler
          An abstract handler for commands that discriminate only between a single file type and create a Runnable for each selected file URI.
WeaveInferringPc2AvMappingHandler
          A handler for the command that weaves the selected base, pointcut and advice models to a new woven model by inferring the mapping from pointcut to advice.
